{"tid":1708023,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[烏克蘭回帶] 開實彈, 只不過係開始","createTime":"2019-11-11T12:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T16:10:42.000Z","uid":121784,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"368eb16a577f5e0761587384fe8736f66391f971","tid":1708023,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:41:33.000Z","msg":"有睇過Winter on Fire嗎?<br />\n<br />\n1. 當時, 烏克蘭革命踏入第2個月. 而第一名示威者死亡, 就係被警察追果時, 由十幾米高處跌下致死...<br />\n<br />\n係唔係好熟口面?<br />\n<br />\n2. 烏克蘭黑警先用棍, 然後到防暴彈, 之後出實彈, 最後用埋狙擊槍. <br />\n<br />\n睇返香港, 林鄭同中央仍然企硬撐警, 可能過幾個月, 會變左實彈放題, 然後出埋自動步槍或狙擊槍,<br />\n變相等同出老解<br />\n<br />\n嬲還嬲, 但更惡劣既形勢可能就係前面.<br />\n大家要有心理準備."},{"pid":"08df35f05f4dde6f46652bd7e743e3c692c7b6d9","tid":1708023,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:44:49.000Z","msg":"我用最卑微嘅態度，求吓你哋<br />\n<br />\n香港人，忍無可忍！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1705050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1705050</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a9459e4d702ecc33a893e8a1ae4fc961f2af51d","tid":1708023,"uid":107656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:48:41.000Z","msg":"我地得把遮<br />\n槍都無把<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6639b22ec55470cde6bc13426b9ba35f3842aab2","tid":1708023,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8509e6688012b4ad80a5e74c06a90c75aec66993","tid":1708023,"uid":308618,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1a9459e4d702ecc33a893e8a1ae4fc961f2af51d","tid":1708023,"uid":107656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:48:41.000Z","msg":"我地得把遮<br />\n槍都無把<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},